name: Awake!
description: Elysium Perdita Collection (Paradise Lost) Genesis - SOUND ON - really this is a collaboration between myself, Domenica Fetti's 'The Veil Of Veronica' (public domain courtesy of National Gallery, and my favorite poet William Blake. Elysium Perdita is focused on a conversation with the art of the past, as an actor I love finding these new mediums for performance and poetry readings, as a poet - any excuse to read my influences and poetic heroes. All unclaimed editions will be burned April 26th.
